data.title: The Best Names in College Football Right Now
data.meta_description: Rowdy Beers and General Booty are just two of the wild names on college football rosters this season. We found the 9 best.
data.text:
So many things make college football awesome: The rivalries, the camaraderie, the bands, the passion ... even the names!

RELATED: The Long-Awaited Video Game Jason Aldean is Excited For

Before the games kick off on Aug. 24, you should get familiar with some of the most unique names in college football for the 2024 season. Maybe Key & Peele were right about this all those years ago.

Rowdy Beers and General Booty are just two of the wild names on college football rosters this season, but keep scrolling to see nine of the very best!
